{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0001", "text": "誰都猜到 我喜歡你吧", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 3, 4, 5, 9, 3, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "dou1", "caai1", "dou3", "ngo5", "hei2", "fun1", "nei5", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "猜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喜歡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0002", "text": "時常發現我 夜深開車 送你歸家", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 4, 2, 5, 2, 3, 3, 3, 4, 5, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["si4", "soeng4", "faat3", "jin6", "ngo5", "je6", "sam1", "hoi1", "ce1", "sung3", "nei5", "gwai1", "gaa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "時常", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發現", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "夜深", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "開車", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "送", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "歸家", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0003", "text": "聽背後有人在說 我沒回家", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 2, 2, 5, 0, 2, 4, 5, 2, 0, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ting1", "bui6", "hau6", "jau5", "jan4", "zoi6", "syut3", "ngo5", "mut6", "wui4", "gaa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "聽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "背後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "回家", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0004", "text": "可惜我沒留下 未曾垂下你窗紗", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 3, 5, 2, 0, 2, 2, 0, 0, 2, 5, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho2", "sik1", "ngo5", "mut6", "lau4", "haa6", "mei6", "cang4", "seoi4", "haa6", "nei5", "coeng1", "saa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "可惜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "留下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "垂下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "窗紗", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0005", "text": "人家怎講 我不管也吧", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 9, 9, 5, 3, 9, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jan4", "gaa1", "zam2", "gong2", "ngo5", "bat1", "gun2", "jaa5", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "人家", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎講", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不管", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0006", "text": "而我在意 是假的可以變真嗎", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 2, 4, 2, 9, 3, 9, 5, 4, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ji4", "ngo5", "zoi6", "ji3", "si6", "gaa2", "dik1", "ho2", "ji5", "bin3", "zan1", "maa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "而", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在意", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "假", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "變真", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0007", "text": "到處亦有人撞過 我在和你交往", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 0, 2, 4, 5, 2, 0, 5, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["dou3", "jik6", "jau5", "jan4", "zong6", "gwo3", "ngo5", "zoi6", "wo4", "nei5", "gaau1", "wong5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "到處", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撞過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "和", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "交往", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0008", "text": "很多緋聞 可惜和你意願 略有偏差", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 3, 3, 0, 9, 3, 0, 5, 4, 2, 2, 5, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["han2", "do1", "fei1", "man4", "ho2", "sik1", "wo4", "nei5", "ji3", "jyun6", "loek6", "jau5", "pin1", "caa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "很多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "緋聞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可惜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "和", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "意願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "略有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "偏差", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0009", "text": "傳聞在說 你正跟我 祕密拍拖", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 5, 4, 3, 5, 4, 2, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cyun4", "man4", "zoi6", "syut3", "nei5", "zing3", "gan1", "ngo5", "bei3", "mat6", "paak3", "to1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "傳聞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "正", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "祕密", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拍拖", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0010", "text": "然而預知了後果 手也未夠膽拖", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 3, 5, 2, 9, 9, 5, 2, 4, 9, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jin4", "ji4", "jyu6", "zi1", "liu5", "hau6", "gwo2", "sau2", "jaa5", "mei6", "gau3", "daam2", "to1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "然而", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "預知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "後果", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "膽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拖", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0011", "text": "要是你心 可以容納我", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 3, 9, 5, 0, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jiu3", "si6", "nei5", "sam1", "ho2", "ji5", "jung4", "naap6", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "要是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "容納", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0012", "text": "何必一拖幾季 還是再拖", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 3, 3, 9, 4, 0, 2, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho4", "bit1", "jat1", "to1", "gei2", "gwai3", "waan4", "si6", "zoi3", "to1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "何必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一拖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幾季", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拖", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0013", "text": "傳聞又說 你會給我 點唱愛歌", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 5, 3, 5, 9, 4, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cyun4", "man4", "jau6", "syut3", "nei5", "kap1", "ngo5", "dim2", "coeng3", "oi3", "go1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "傳聞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "點唱", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛歌", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0014", "text": "來回地聽了十遍 都不似送給我", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 3, 5, 2, 4, 3, 3, 5, 4, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["loi4", "wui4", "dei6", "ting1", "liu5", "sap6", "pin3", "dou1", "bat1", "ci5", "sung3", "kap1", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "來回", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "十遍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不似", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "送給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "緋聞男友", "artists": ["劉浩龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5292", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YiY5rWp6b6Z_NTI5Mg_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
